# CK-NEXUS AIOS Enterprise Monorepo

## Turborepo Configuration

```json
{
  "$schema": "https://turbo.build/schema.json",
  "pipeline": {
    "build": {
      "dependsOn": ["^build"],
      "outputs": ["dist/**", "build/**"]
    },
    "dev": {
      "cache": false,
      "persistent": true
    },
    "test": {
      "dependsOn": [],
      "outputs": ["coverage/**"]
    },
    "lint": {},
    "test:unit": {
      "outputs": ["coverage/**"]
    },
    "test:integration": {
      "dependsOn": ["build"]
    },
    "test:e2e": {
      "dependsOn": ["build", "docker:up"]
    }
  },
  "globalEnv": ["NODE_ENV", "PYTHONPATH", "CK_NEXUS_CONFIG"]
}
```